data.chText: 体育运动的；田径运动的
data.enText: connected with sports such as running, jumping and throwing (= athletics )

data.chText: 运动员俱乐部 / 教练
她在球场上矫健地奔跑活动。
data.enText: She moved with great athleticism about the court.

simple_means.memory_skill: athl 比赛 + etic 关于…的 → 运动的

ex.chText: 他是个体格健壮的赛跑运动员。
45岁的他身体健壮，有着30岁小伙子的体能。
ex.enText: He is an athletic 45-year-old man with the body of a 30-year-old.

synonyms.bx: 指身强体壮、健康活跃且擅长体育运动的。

ex.chText: 他手臂上的肌肉非常结实。
ex.enText: The muscles of his arms are very brawny/muscular.

ex.chText: 他那肌肉发达的胸部像铁一样结实。
ex.enText: His brawny/muscular chest is as strong as iron.

synonyms.bx: 指身体魁梧健壮、肌肉发达的，常可与 muscular 换用。

ex.chText: 她的丈夫英俊潇洒，身体强壮。
ex.enText: Her husband is handsome and muscular.

ex.chText: 他有着肌肉发达的手臂。

tr: having a sturdy and well proportioned body
relating to or befitting athletics or athletes

value.def: Athletic means relating to athletes and athletics.

example.ex: They have been given college scholarships purely on athletic ability...
example.tran: 他们完全是凭体育特长才获得了大学奖学金。

example.ex: Most athletic activities are about individual effort.
example.tran: 大多数体育项目是靠个人的拼搏。

value.tran: 运动的;体育的;运动员的

example.tran: 她学业优秀，体育方面也很突出。

value.def: An athletic person is fit, and able to perform energetic movements easily.

example.ex: Xandra is an athletic 36-year-old with a 21-year-old's body...
example.tran: 36岁的汉德拉身体健壮，有着21岁小伙子的体能。

example.ex: He was tall, with an athletic build.
He jumped athletically out of the car.
example.tran: 他身手矫捷地跳出了车子。

trans: 竞技运动；体育运动；田径运动
毕尔巴鄂竞技；毕尔包；毕尔巴鄂；畢爾包；毕尔巴鄂竞技俱乐部
运动训练师；运动治疗师；运动防护师；训练师
